      <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="webimages/ggibson.jpeg" width="180" height="217" border="1" /></p>
    </blockquote>
    </td>
    <td width="364"> 
      <p><b><font size="2">Consulting Professor<br />
      </font></b>Computer Science Department, CMU</p>
      <p><strong>Chief Technology and AI Officer</strong><br>
Vdura Inc.</p>
      <p><strong>Adjunct Professor, Department of Computer Science</strong><br>
University of Toronto<br>
        <br/>
        <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><font size="2">      garth dot gibson @ cs dot cmu dot edu</font></font></p>
     <p><b>Past Courses Taught:</b><br>
       <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~410/">15-410 Operating Systems Design and Implementation</a><br>
       <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~15712/">15-712 Advanced and Distributed Operating Systems</a><br>
       <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~15719/">15-719 Advanced Cloud Computing</a><br>
